{"url": "https://www.popsugar.com/latina/What-Does-Bidi-Bidi-Bom-Bom-Mean-43978290", "text": "Selena's song \"Bidi Bidi Bom Bom\" is a hit that we all know every single word to. The tune was released as part of her album Amor Prohibido on July 31, 1994, and has been on repeat at every Latinx household ever since \u2014 but did you ever stop to wonder what the lyrics of the song mean? We have the answer from Selena herself.\n\nIn an interview with Don Francisco on S\u00e1bado Gigante in 1994, the late Tejana singer talked about the catchy chorus of her new song. She revealed she was actually the one who wrote the song and what the special meaning behind it was.\n\n\"It's the sound the heart makes when you see a man pass by. It sounds like, 'Bidi bidi bom bom,'\" Selena told Don Francisco. According to Selena's brother, A.B. Quintanilla, she wrote the song shortly after Chris P\u00e9rez joined Los Dinos, so it all makes sense, right?\n\n\"Bidi Bidi Bom Bom\" was an instant winner and became even more iconic after Selena's untimely death, becoming a favorite cover by the likes of Jennifer Lopez and Kat Von D.", "images": ["https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/YjOxdFGhi1UIn0mWcXmktG8yxuQ/fit-in/1200x630/filters:format_auto-!!-:strip_icc-!!-:fill-!white!-/2017/09/05/903/n/37139775/85cdde9b59af0bbb1de291.09475158_edit_img_facebook_post_image_file_43978290_1504643635.jpg", "https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/mAHP0QD7fWUndy1h99D1v_RpbII/0x0:2133x2133/fit-in/550x550/filters:format_auto-!!-:strip_icc-!!-/2022/03/14/560/n/44490375/21544c09622f34aa475d76.95424887_/i/lashana-lynch-facts.jpg", "https://media1.popsugar-assets.com/files/thumbor/Sflug0qn5WS0-tYkuTiGso-p5rs/fit-in/550x550/filters:format_auto-!!-:strip_icc-!!-/2022/03/14/802/n/1922398/tmp_QDIMrB_d773126a0c218cf9_GettyImages-1384952499/i/hoyeon-jung-visits-euphoria-set-with-zendaya.jpg", "https://www.facebook.com/tr?id=258101201039378&ev=PageView&noscript=1", "https://media1.popsugar-assets.co